                    <span>This amazing cookbook has helped me lose eight hundred pounds. It's taught me how to use bread for sandwiches rather than two twinkies, how to make my famous "artery clogger chilli" without five sticks of butter. It's changed my life so much i don't know how to thank you guys at amazon[.com] for bringing it to my door.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">150 Ways to Ruin Food with Vinegar, Salsa, and Worcester</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>48</span>
                      /
                      <span>49</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
